title: Manny Pacquiao
summary: Emmanuel Dapidran Pacquiao Sr., CLH (locally [pɐkˈjaʊ]; born December 17, 1978) is a Filipino politician and former professional boxer.[5] Nicknamed "PacMan", he is regarded as one of the greatest professional boxers of all time.[6] He has been serving as a senator of the Philippines since 2016.
